        <title>The <reference internal="True" refid="module-glance.common.auth" reftitle="glance.common.auth"><literal classes="xref py py-mod">glance.common.auth</literal></reference> Module</title>
        <index entries="['single',\ u'glance.common.auth\ (module)',\ u'module-glance.common.auth',\ '',\ None]"></index>
        <paragraph>This auth module is intended to allow OpenStack client-tools to select from a
            variety of authentication strategies, including NoAuth (the default), and
            Keystone (an identity management system).</paragraph>
        <block_quote>
            <paragraph>&gt; auth_plugin = AuthPlugin(creds)</paragraph>
            <paragraph>&gt; auth_plugin.authenticate()</paragraph>
            <paragraph>&gt; auth_plugin.auth_token
                abcdefg</paragraph>
            <paragraph>&gt; auth_plugin.management_url
                <reference refuri="http://service_endpoint/">http://service_endpoint/</reference></paragraph>
        </block_quote>
