                <paragraph>Select an endpoint from the service catalog</paragraph>
                <paragraph>We search the full service catalog for services
                    matching both type and region. If the client
                    supplied no region then any ‘image’ endpoint
                    is considered a match. There must be one – and
                    only one – successful match in the catalog,
                    otherwise we will raise an exception.</paragraph>
